stitched in England. My mother burnt all
her saris. They used to spin their own

5
00:00:32,938 --> 00:00:40,456
clothes and wear them. I had only one coat
throughout My education, when I was in Lahore,

6
00:00:40,456 --> 00:00:48,487
which is terribly cold, sometimes can be
like London. But we never grudged and

7
00:00:48,487 --> 00:00:52,118
