for the country?" Never, never, never.

9
00:00:58,552 --> 00:01:09,462
That quality was created, I should say, by
Mahatma Gandhi. He made everybody so

10
00:01:09,462 --> 00:01:18,325
transformed into a new personality. All the
money that we had, everything that we had,

11
00:01:18,325 --> 00:01:25,578
all conveniences, all housing, everything
was given up, not only by My father but

12
00:01:25,578 --> 00:01:35,644
so many of them otherwise we could not
have got our freedom. To get our freedom

13
00:01:36,216 --> 00:01:44,366
this country has sacrificed so much.
I must say, Gandhiji had a special charm.

14
00:01:45,197 --> 00:01:53,017
I don't know how he managed. He was like
'Touch of Midas', touched anybody, he
became transformed, you see.

15
00:01:57,387 --> 00:02:03,767
And he was an extremely strict man - very
kind to Me, to children - but he was an

16
00:02:03,767 --> 00:02:10,025
