of or independence but even before that for
spiritual life, anywhere, there's one thing

19
00:02:29,761 --> 00:02:35,416
very common, is sacrifice and the
consciousness that you are doing

20
00:02:35,416 --> 00:02:41,026
something great, consciouness that you
